{"tid":1611503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣大和理非們，你願意繼續保護學生嗎？","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:59:32.000Z","uid":56260,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"84c7b4447ab7b8a493fae3c459a90172b94eaaff","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"首先我地需要承認四件事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 政府同黑警係唔會為佢地既行為道歉同負責<br />\n2. 高調既鎮壓令到好多本身敢於上街既和理非卻步<br />\n3. 自9月罷課同人鏈活動起，動員重心向學生轉移<br />\n4. 國際戰線既支持遠水不能救近火</span></span><br />\n<br />\n近四個月黎，黑警既手段係越趨高壓<br />\n就算執勤既黑警點樣瘋狂暴躁，你係吹佢唔脹<br />\n媒體上幾多尖銳既批評，對佢地既影響已經飽和<br />\n莫講話黑警自己，連同路人都會怕睇到麻木<br />\n所以除左鬧之餘，我地要做更多既實事！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 用金錢狠狠地懲罰黃店</span></strong></span><br />\n[戰術] 大家必需善待黃店, 先有更多店敢黃!! 創造黃經濟圈!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611238/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611238/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2. 保護手足，人數重要既活動，盡量參與</strong></span></span><br />\n無論係法院聲援、修補連儂牆、學生罷課、人鏈、集會等<br />\n盡量現身出席，就算唔參與都盡量逗留附近，監察形勢<br />\n［警世］10.1以後，開真槍會變常態<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611151/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611151/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3. 時刻提高警覺，互相照應</strong></span></span><br />\n加入各大地區TG group，有咩風吹草動就互相通報<br />\nlink就唔特別喺度po，自己搵下屋企或者常去既地區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>4. 大大力抵制親中商戶</strong></span></span><br />\n最容易做既事，每一個人徹底地做、持久地做，先越快見效<br />\n勇武抗爭 經濟抗爭 雙管齊下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611325/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611325/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5. Twitter長期要人，宣掦警暴、對抗五毛</span></strong></span><br />\n請入 @TwitterHelpBot, 然後打 /task 就可以見到任務了。到現在已領任務的人數為 XXXX<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNh6VoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNh6VoB.jpg&h=1fb85e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[國際文宣]喺Twitter只要有一萬Retweet同Like已經好勁，香港人應該好易做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1603472/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1603472/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>6. 繼續打爆和理非bingo紙</strong></span></span><br />\n一路做緊既事，繼續做<br />\n未做既，搵機會試下做<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKwLrwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKwLrwq.jpg&h=16703e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>相信大家都同意，黃絲都有好多種層次<br />\n可唔可以同自己講，積極提升自己既層次<br />\n令整股勢力可以達到最大既效用？</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n唔止係口號 你我都有份將佢實行</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學生值得你地每一位更多既參與</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1a31adb9b88ed0dc81ebe3bcdd29240191c30520","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bc3418ddd71661b3e4d01f6591903a46d40d969","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6db99fd0d0ee17f5cb2fb97525543262088fcdde","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85435012ae5b2e1cb19ae1091423bb3fa606598","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3f22c322af9859add93edf14f484f1dfda3c38f","tid":1611503,"uid":72654,"like":0,"dislike