/>\n盡量現身出席，就算唔參與都盡量逗留附近，監察形勢<br />\n［警世］10.1以後，開真槍會變常態<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611151/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611151/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3. 時刻提高警覺，互相照應</strong></span></span><br />\n加入各大地區TG group，有咩風吹草動就互相通報<br />\nlink就唔特別喺度po，自己搵下屋企或者常去既地區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>4. 大大力抵制親中商戶</strong></span></span><br />\n最容易做既事，每一個人徹底地做、持久地做，先越快見效<br />\n勇武抗爭 經濟抗爭 雙管齊下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611325/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611325/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5. Twitter長期要人，宣掦警暴、對抗五毛</span></strong></span><br />\n請入 @TwitterHelpBot, 然後打 /task 就可以見到任務了。到現在已領任務的人數為 XXXX<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNh6VoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNh6VoB.jpg&h=1fb85e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[國際文宣]喺Twitter只要有一萬Retweet同Like已經好勁，香港人應該好易做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1603472/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1603472/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>6. 繼續打爆和理非bingo紙</strong></span></span><br />\n一路做緊既事，繼續做<br />\n未做既，搵機會試下做<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKwLrwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKwLrwq.jpg&h=16703e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>相信大家都同意，黃絲都有好多種層次<br />\n可唔可以同自己講，積極提升自己既層次<br />\n令整股勢力可以達到最大既效用？</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n唔止係口號 你我都有份將佢實行</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學生值得你地每一位更多既參與</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:23:37.000Z","msg":"我要間間藍店都無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776b5bff9b095b674fc6a210f9366f58f668c347","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a915acade9a924e4d3a581e490ac726b1ada4e5","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9800073790c1a033cb8d07678b44f93ff1ab2d55","tid":1611503,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"964818be5f58e2dbcd3c7c84e69a8012b04b02b4","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c354cb51152bf792c3899ac7de5942b58d9eba3","tid":1611503,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6f7ad935523171b03e00a7100783ac88e2abc42","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25a9f29cddec1d6557e10df1139efe6c087baf6d","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4def4ae6e3522df4be0144ccd33a707d89666fd","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:31:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d713d64678bb553e6f3562c9b9353b71f9f8d9e","tid":1611503,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n唔好再指責所謂偽勇武 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611678</a>"},{"pid":"fdd62ce4b321756c5d0eff479bbf39a30bf59494","tid":1611503,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ae1ff99ea7b1f1405206affc3a0b3f66737d81","tid":1611503,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78ba399364da810a9e2c0634005135d177d45a5","tid":1611503,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"和理非仲有好多嘢未做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bb2f24033cfcac74f7927119a3aa7f91474ce3","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d78ba399364da810a9e2c0634005135d177d45a5","tid":1611503,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"和理非仲有好多嘢未做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"身邊有好多和理非好灰<br />\n一齊繼續做大佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b144a1b38f560011c8efa0ec030b94b58392ef","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cab1e9a46dd5e997acc3d9cce4b3b67a13e37e9e","tid":1611503,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"簽撚哂佢<br />\n乜柒都要做<br />\n<br />\n《美國白宮聯署》<br />\n<br />\n差佬已經開真槍謀殺，我哋真係急需救援！<br />\n<br />\n簽完後，記得在 email 裏 click confirm！<br />\n<br />\n1. 請求美國行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁侵犯人權的香港官員或知名人士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mIGUn2&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=7641e74d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2</a><br />\n尚欠 50000 人聯署，10 月 10 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n2. 請求美國拯救香港市民，提供人道救援<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kk2ZHW&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=a3956968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW</a><br />\n尚欠 2000 人聯署，10 月 11 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 請求美國通過《香港保護法案》，暫停向香港警察出售催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈和其他防暴物品。<br />\n尚欠 70000 人聯署，10 月 14 日截止。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m39jUJ&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=bd54af7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 請求美國將香港警察加入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單。<br />\n尚欠 73000 人聯署，10 月 16 日截止。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyBsT1&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=d61e579d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 請求美國承認香港為美國保護區。<br />\n尚欠 75000 人聯署，10 月 20 日截止。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kK8y2q&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=61faf09e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q</a>"},{"pid":"033b93a122f1e814fb74b20e7ef233316fd4d38f","tid":1611503,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d16f94cb7237741e2fa0fac4436edb91e023b8c2","tid":1611503,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T0